| [HALiveActivityWidget.swift](file:///c:/Users/gaschler/AntiGravity/iOS/Sources/Extensions/Widgets/LiveActivity/HALiveActivityWidget.swift) | `ActivityConfiguration` widget struct registered in widget bundles |

